node.text: My self care tip is to take time out for myself, to take a breather and let go of all the negativity in my life. Have more me-time for myself and take a break to relax and rejuvenate by doing the things that I love and enjoy the most, like putting on a facial mask while listening to my favourite music & lightening up a scented candle because when I do that, it certainly makes me a more happier person ☺️ @scottssquaresg @jollyjoy921 @glchiam @jongohws
Do what I love for eg painting, get enough rest and do yoga with my wife! @rainbowshines83 @pyloveschh @potatoheheheh @scottssquaresg

It’s Day 42 of the Circuit Breaker. Comment below 👇 with 3 self-care tips (e.g., reading, exercising 🧘‍♀️ or baking 👩‍🍳 etc) that have helped you during this period! 10 lucky winners will be randomly selected to win $50 worth of Scotts Square shopping vouchers each, to be collected and used when the Circuit Breaker period is over.

All you have to do is:
1) Comment with 3 self-care tips 👇
2) Follow and tag our account @scottssquaresg
3) Tag 3 friends whom you’ll want to share this with

Contest ends on 24 May 2020, 1159pm. Winners will be announced on 25 May 2020, 6pm. Visit https://bit.ly/SSQSelfCare for contest terms and conditions.
.

❤️ Quality me-time over a hot bath with Lush bath bomb & apply a hair mask to moisturise my hair so that it is smooth, flowy, shiny & luscious! .
❤️ De-stress, chill & relax by putting on a cold hyaluronic mask on my face straight from the fridge to moisturise & hydrate my skin for luminous, radiant, glowing skin & a brighter complexion!
.
❤ Cut off from fake & toxic friends who use & abuse me and take advantage of my kindness & good heart! Mental health and emotional health affects my physical health and well-being! Surround myself with friends who love me and support me instead! ♥️ @stephaniewong35 @matthew_tan368 @jiahui508 @scottssquaresg

My self-care tips are:
.
1️⃣ Get plenty of quality restful sleep & eat well (fruits, veggies, Kombucha, probiotics, etc)
.
2️⃣ Listen to classical music which is calming, relaxing & soothing to my mind, body & soul. Listening to Baroque music brings peace and tranquility to my entire being - spirit, soul & body!
.
3️⃣ Drink a glass of iced cold coconut water or sugarcane juice to beat the heat and humidity & hydrate my body!💧💧
.
